title: ATOMIC COWBOYS (Flash Game)
description:
ATOMIC COWBOYS The Game

Shoot, run and triple jump your way through a monsters and laser shooting robots infected lab. Rescue scientist along the way, grab a life or two. A game based on the  digital comic Atomic Cowboys.
